# Single source of truth for the pinned Pandoc render image — a digest, so the
# PDF render is reproducible. Sourced by scripts/render_pdf.sh (which pre-pulls
# it) and scripts/pandoc-docker.sh (the shim arqix's [policies.render]
# pdf-command invokes), so a pin bump lands in one place and both stay in sync.
# Override by exporting PANDOC_IMAGE before either script runs.
: "${PANDOC_IMAGE:=pandoc/extra@sha256:dfae5cf73a0e0ad40acf23d2d2c4adf5715e560aeea3324aa87e68faaa2e70c9}"
